item.description:
I'll be there at least a half hour early. Jason is quite popular, so Vincent's will most likely fill up fast. Come early if you can. BTW - Vincent's has one of the best meatball sandwiches in Worcester County. If you love a good meatball, come hungry!

There will most likely not be a cover charge, but they'll probably "pass the bucket," so plan on tossing five bucks in and you've gotten a great deal!
item.how_to_find_us: One of us will have a meetup sign in plain sight.
item.name: Jason James and the Bay State House Rockers
